title: AU Small Finance Q4 Net Profit seen up 87.6% YoY to Rs. 316.9 cr: Motilal Oswal - Moneycontrol
content: AU Small Finance Q4 Net Profit seen up 87.6% YoY to Rs. 316.9 cr: Motilal Oswal  Moneycontrol
description: Net Interest Income (NII) is expected to increase by 36.4 percent Y-o-Y (up 9 percent Q-o-Q) to Rs. 895.4 crore, according to Motilal Oswal.
